reviewText:
The things I like:
1) different islands with different missions;
2) you have your own carrier that you can controll and command from and ship from island to island;
3) the supply and production factor is nice;
4) hability to control the different vehicles;

I really want to like this game but there are three things that make me not to:
1) Your own vehicle AI is terribly bad: It gets stuck, it faces away from the enemy, sometimes it just stares and locks the enemy without shotting it, and I checked, there wasplenty of ammo.
2) I think some of the island missions were not test played, example: this mission where we need to take the air defenses first with walrusses . Well.. there is this one air defense which is unreachible by land.. I spent 3 hours blindly trying to mortar it with grenades.. I felt it was not a very nice way to send gaming time.
3) You cannot play with your own human player.. only sometimes.. and when you do you cannot command the other units at the same time.
4) Cannot map my mouse keys.. what?
5) no coop.. what a miss.
